2995661e1983bff6fbe04a4616c8a93626485","tid":495173,"uid":162445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做過眼手術<br />\n用刀搞個眼球個隻<br />\n好小事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打可唔可以詳細啲分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b1b4bc8a415265a309d585c42ff56d19915185","tid":495173,"uid":93640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比人打唔報警仲要自己出十萬去醫?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打 有時啲嘢係好複雜 原諒我不能講太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你盡快去做手術啦, 祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c7beaf9bed7c1526af2d0fa34f46773f5fb958","tid":495173,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做過眼手術<br />\n用刀搞個眼球個隻<br />\n好小事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打可唔可以詳細啲分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無咩好分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> take it easy <br />\n我個時只係局部麻醉<br />\n係做完之後痛撚咗兩星期囉"},{"pid":"cfa8509e27ffd27ac477c990bcdfeed459fe1e88","tid":495173,"uid":38765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n雖然冇做過有關手術<br />\n但睇哂成段野有少少sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望巴打快啲冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8a3b0caa387b416d5f621a77706e4b824312f1","tid":495173,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T15:01:08.000Z","msg":"叫打你果個比"},{"pid":"12ddd571e9dc6e0f3741cee28a52dcc8911d98ae","tid":495173,"uid":55445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"10皮如果私家做一個全身麻醉手術唔算貴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37103acb8fe12799428f77b6f359f9a51f9a4fb9","tid":495173,"uid":5056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"淨係講全身麻醉其實無乜野<br />\n吸兩淡氣就會訓著，到手術完左先會醒<br />\n最多都係醒返勁口渴<br />\n你都係擔心返個手術本身啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比我揀我一定做"},{"pid":"5dd2ffdb56f5c748dbece92062f7ac7d9364cbd0","tid":495173,"uid":146631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"唔想報驚因為俾屋企人打？"},{"pid":"1cc199247295ebbd0bd3b982e1942e2e2b04c3a1","tid":495173,"uid":25279,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T15:42:56.000Z","msg":"巴打你廿幾歲人喇，唔好做乜決定都阿媽前阿媽後啦<br />\n雖然字裡行間都估到你係俾屋企人打成咁<br />\n但十萬蚊換返隻眼同個樣真係唔貴，求其打份工半年都搵到呢個數，唔好再拖個手術喇，免得後悔一世"},{"pid":"f6f23ceed96e76548a03bd2607411080595edae2","tid":495173,"uid":10453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T15:47:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打 <br />\n呀媽話不如睇多個醫生再決定去唔去公立 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以分享下你全身麻醉嘅心路歷程 <br />\n我真係好驚好驚好驚嗰隻 一諗起就想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直接去公立啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你去公立都係睇多次醫生姐<br />\n你自己都識講黃金時期啦<br />\n就算你去公立都可能即刻同你做手術<br />\n而家骨折呀，貴都要做架啦，唔做既你遲d搵到錢但已經毀容+長期痛你仲後悔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好聽老母講，十個老母九個troll<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nX2 ......</blockquote><br />\nbtw...你去到急症...醫生會問你點整襯...你唔係撞車..唔係仆街(但你額頭又無事)..又唔係成....好難會eye socket fracture...你有定心理準備 佢會搵急症室station差佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打心水清 <br />\n呢個就係老母一開始唔肯去急症嘅原因 <br />\n本身家庭醫生寫轉介信 老母同我去私立醫院<br />\n點知話比人打唔接受 唔肯睇 登記錢都蝕埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返返去睇家庭醫生開啲消炎止痛藥比我先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同你老母講，避唔到架啦.....就算急症室放過你...醫生無搵差佬<br />\n你上到病房,收症醫生都會有懷疑...實問硬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係領養返嚟？"},{"pid":"8735e2da6e957be9fcbdbcbaf7496fdd6dd2eceb","tid":495173,"uid":34295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"鼓啦，下次打死你"},{"pid":"21d57de49d6b277e4957abb4d51266ba406c3454","tid":495173,"uid":162445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:18:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫打你果個比</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4da970a19daa559734469825fec21ae2f18faf","tid":495173,"uid":162445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想報驚因為俾屋企人打？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10bad29d273f70e48a12f4ae2c1e3441fd6fd02","tid":495173,"uid":162445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:21:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你廿幾歲人喇，唔好做乜決定都阿媽前阿媽後啦<br />\n雖然字裡行間都估到你係俾屋企人打成咁<br />\n但十萬蚊換返隻眼同個樣真係唔貴，求其打份工半年都搵到呢個數，唔好再拖個手術喇，免得後悔一世</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6e2259714683c03feb9ae1b857b8c42078c110","tid":495173,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:22:19.000Z","msg":"男人塊面有疤形好多喎"},{"pid":"d20a3dea921d20c9c52ecc9236359e3d30c16aa9","tid":495173,"uid":162445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n直接去公立啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你去公立都係睇多次醫生姐<br />\n你自己都識講黃金時期啦<br />\n就算你去公立都可能即刻同你做手術<br />\n而家骨折呀，貴都要做架啦，唔做既你遲d搵到錢但已經毀容+長期痛你仲後悔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好聽老母講，十個老母九個troll<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nX2 ......</blockquote><br />\nbtw...你去到急症...醫生會問你點整襯...你唔係撞車..唔係仆街(但你額頭又無事)..又唔係成....好難會eye socket fracture...你有定心理準備 佢會搵急症室station差佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打心水清 <br />\n呢個就係老母一開始唔肯去急症嘅原因 <br />\n本身家庭醫生寫轉介信 老母同我去私立醫院<br />\n點知話比人打唔接受 唔肯睇 登記錢都蝕埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返返去睇家庭醫生開啲消炎止痛藥比我先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同你老母講，避唔到架啦.....就算急症室放過你...醫生無搵差佬<br />\n你上到病房,收症醫生都會有懷疑...實問硬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係領養返嚟？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035cf09c36261f83dd3aa3d73e1a947d800288db","tid":495173,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你廿幾歲人喇，唔好做乜決定都阿媽前阿媽後啦<br />\n雖然字裡行間都估到你係俾屋企人打成咁<br />\n但十萬蚊換返隻眼同個樣真係唔貴，求其打份工半年都搵到呢個數，唔好再拖個手術喇，免得後悔一世</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f74e9242d06697a984135253c30c3437b8af7e","tid":495173,"uid":60536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:25:45.000Z","msg":"推咗先 好少聽人講做依個手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f278445384074a3ad06098f23a1fda2baaba366","tid":495173,"uid":162445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:27:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人塊面有疤形好多喎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d6e01d7459a1991292bc3374b8e4ca29a6776e","tid":495173,"uid":16036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n直接去公立啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你去公立都係睇多次醫生姐<br />\n你自己都識講黃金時期啦<br />\n就算你去公立都可能即刻同你做手術<br />\n而家骨折呀，貴都要做架啦，唔做既你遲d搵到錢但已經毀容+長期痛你仲後悔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好聽老母講，十個老母九個troll<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nX2 ......</blockquote><br />\nbtw...你去到急症...醫生會問你點整襯...你唔係撞車..唔係仆街(但你額頭又無事)..又唔係成....好難會eye socket fracture...你有定心理準備 佢會搵急症室station差佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打心水清 <br />\n呢個就係老母一開始唔肯去急症嘅原因 <br />\n本身家庭醫生寫轉介信 老母同我去私立醫院<br />\n點知話比人打唔接受 唔肯睇 登記錢都蝕埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返返去睇家庭醫生開啲消炎止痛藥比我先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同你老母講，避唔到架啦.....就算急症室放過你...醫生無搵差佬<br />\n你上到病房,收症醫生都會有懷疑...實問硬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔搞大件事 自己咪大件事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人打仲要拎十萬出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心戇鳩 呢個時侯重要做愚孝撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾人打唔報警重要自己拎十萬出黎？<br />\n巴打你訓撚醒未 定係俾人打到傻左<br />\n老母叫你做乜就做乜 咁你咪繼續聽老母講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e0d8ae7ff9074f4e8308d3b73e812354c4cebd","tid":495173,"uid":119446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:38:00.000Z","msg":"屌你隻眼有事整就整<br />\n又驚有疤又盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf61a85047f38efcde5ba26c450af82b5a2a467","tid":495173,"uid":7458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"眼呢d野盲左就一世架啦<br />\n你唔係7/80歲 仲有幾十年命等你<br />\n你真係可以接受到之後果幾十年隻眼keep住有事??"},{"pid":"4156a56c70b4aee612324d6345219061c5fa2b58","tid":495173,"uid":514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:40:19.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"1a08b1d1c4230505a6c4e44cf84bfaab4871e5e2","tid":495173,"uid":23445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"其他唔講,<br />\n手術費+所有住院同醫療雜項 要十萬<br />\n<br />\n其實唔貴啦,仲要專科<br />\n依家cool牙都要3,4萬"},{"pid":"67d1743498860019d8b4169c0e887b1705ad185f","tid":495173,"uid":28250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T16:49:23.000Z","msg":"梗係做啦<br />\n其實麻醉唔恐怖, 你咪當訓一覺<br />\n起返就已經做完手術"},{"pid":"97873c77b8dd1183ae69411e44a825da5898bf93","tid":495173,"uid":162445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nX2 ......</blockquote><br />\nbtw...你去到急症...醫生會問你點整襯...你唔係撞車..唔係仆街(但你額頭又無事)..又唔係成....好難會eye socket fracture...你有定心理準備 佢會搵急症室station差佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打心水清 <br />\n呢個就係老母一開始唔肯去急症嘅原因 <br />\n本身家庭醫生寫轉介信 老母同我去私立醫院<br />\n點知話比人打唔接受 唔肯睇 登記錢都蝕埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返返去睇家庭醫生開啲消炎止痛藥比我先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同你老母講，避唔到架啦.....就算急症室放過你...醫生無搵差佬<br />\n你上到病房,收症醫生都會有懷疑...實問硬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔搞大件事 自己咪大件事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人打仲要拎十萬出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心戇鳩 呢個時侯重要做愚孝撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾人打唔報警重要自己拎十萬出黎？<br />\n巴打你訓撚醒未 定係俾人打到傻左<br />\n老母叫你做乜就做乜 咁你咪繼續聽老母講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打可以睇返上面啲回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9edf86622791c3b9af6cab748e0bbdf7f328d44","tid":495173,"uid":162445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T17:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你隻眼有事整就整<br />\n又驚有疤又盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n驚有疤其次<br />\n係本身對做手術嘅恐懼 <br />\n同埋根本search唔到有關呢方面手術嘅案例 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17821efe31816fb18a749f9eb73ee19e5254b2e","tid":495173,"uid":162445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T17:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梗係做啦<br />\n其實麻醉唔恐怖, 你咪當訓一覺<br />\n起返就已經做完手術</blockquote><br />\n巴打有經驗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811f429b05b9cd5ddec99bdeccc326803e64a8e1","tid":495173,"uid":52162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T17:30:55.000Z","msg":"全身麻醉無嘢，我都試過喇，嗰次都係做眼上面"}]}